snippet.title: Stray Blade - Gameplay Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2022
snippet.description: Stray Blade is an Action RPG where you play a rogue Adventurer exploring the ancient Valley of Acrea with your companion, the Xhinnon wolf Boji. Stray Blade is coming to PC, PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X and S in 2023.
